OL,3,CGrooming gang members' 'unduly
OL,4,Clenient' sentences increased
OL,6,FThree members of a grooming gang who
OL,7,Fwere convicted of sexually abusing a
OL,8,Fvulnerable girl have had their 'unduly
OL,9,Flenient' sentences increased.
OL,11,FIbrar Hussain, and brothers Imtiaz
OL,12,FAhmed and Fayaz Ahmed, were jailed for
OL,13,Fsix-and-a-half years, nine years, and
OL,14,Fseven-and-a-half years at Bradford
OL,15,FCrown Court in January.
OL,17,FThey were convicted of raping a girl
OL,18,Fin Keighley, West Yorkshire, in the
OL,19,F1990s, when she was 13 or 14.
