OL,3,CGrooming gang members' 'unduly
OL,4,Clenient' sentences increased
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, the Court of Appeal
OL,7,Fincreased Hussain's sentence for two
OL,8,Fcounts of rape to 10 years, and Imtiaz
OL,9,FAhmed's to 11 years for one count of
OL,10,Frape.
OL,12,FFayaz Ahmed's sentence was increased
OL,13,Fto 10 years for two counts of rape.
OL,15,FTheir sentences had been referred to
OL,16,Fthe Court of Appeal by the Solicitor
OL,17,FGeneral under the Unduly Lenient
OL,18,FSentence Scheme.
