OL,6,FOn Wednesday Robert Jenrick, shadow
OL,7,Fjustice secretary, welcomed the
OL,8,Fincrease in the sentences, writing on
OL,9,FX:
OL,11,F"Yesterday the Court of Appeal found
OL,12,Fthat these sentences were more than
OL,13,Funduly lenient - they were
OL,14,Fsignificantly so.
