OL,3,CGrooming gang members' 'unduly
OL,4,Clenient' sentences increased
OL,6,F"It is deeply troubling that these
OL,7,Fthree offenders were part of a wider
OL,8,Fgroup tried for similar abuse. But the
OL,9,Fstatutory window for referring the
OL,10,Fother five sentences under the Unduly
OL,11,FLenient Sentence scheme has now
OL,12,Fexpired."
OL,14,FDuring the hearing, Lord Justice
OL,15,FStuart-Smith, with Mrs Justice Eady
OL,16,Fand Mr Justice Cavanagh, heard the
OL,17,Fvictim met the men in the early 1990s,
OL,18,Fand was supplied with money, drugs and
OL,19,Falcohol in return for sex.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
