OL,6,FShe was taken to various places where
OL,7,Fshe was raped over several years,
OL,8,Fincluding by Hussain and the Ahmed
OL,9,Fbrothers.
OL,11,FIbrar Hussain and Fayaz Ahmed were 18
OL,12,Fand 17 respectively when they carried
OL,13,Fout their offences, and Imtiaz Ahmed
OL,14,Fwas in his 30s.
OL,16,FSolicitor General Lucy Rigby said:
OL,17,F"This case involved the shocking and
OL,18,Fhideous abuse of a vulnerable teenager
OL,19,Fby these three sexual predators.
